          {
            "speaker": "lucena",
            "target": "saiki",
            "line": "I checked everything out~ The peddler's lock is toy-level, and the sword guy is the type who won't let go of his blade even in his sleep. But that hooded person over there... has zero luggage. Isn't that suspicious?",
            "tone": "playful+whisper",
